personal.backstory:
Her Royal Majesty Queen Quicksilver of Cinobubia.
Forced to marry the evil queen Dak Bleth against her will under duress as Dak Bleth held her people hostage with the plague.

Secret leader of the resistance, she has asked your help in the war to end Dak Bleth's reign, there is very little love lost in her marriage.

core.name: Fist
core.description: Throw a barehanded punch with fist.
